        <h1 class="post-title" itemprop="name headline">
          搭建 VMware 共享文件夹
        </h1>

        <div class="post-meta">
            <span class="post-meta-item">
              <span class="post-meta-item-icon">
                <i class="far fa-calendar"></i>
              </span>
              <span class="post-meta-item-text">Posted on</span>

              <time title="Created: 2021-11-03 16:48:49" itemprop="dateCreated datePublished" datetime="2021-11-03T16:48:49+08:00">2021-11-03</time>
            </span>
              <span class="post-meta-item">
                <span class="post-meta-item-icon">
                  <i class="far fa-calendar-check"></i>
                </span>
                <span class="post-meta-item-text">Edited on</span>
                <time title="Modified: 2022-04-08 16:01:05" itemprop="dateModified" datetime="2022-04-08T16:01:05+08:00">2022-04-08</time>
              </span>
            <span class="post-meta-item">
